measurements.description: Eleven flat flowers on one 78-cm arching inflorescence; sepals obovate, yellow sparsely speckled burgundy; petals eliptical, yellow, sparsely speckled burgundy, burgundy midrib; lip white overlaid burgundy reverse, marked burgundy heavily apical third, center burgundy stripe, sparsely spotted burgundy proximal two-thirds, densely speckled burgundy mid-lobe edges, keels yellow spotted burgundy; column cream, overlaid burgundy, spotted burgundy ventral surface, anther cap white; substance firm; texture matte.
